             was indicted for <rs id="t18170702-82-off466" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18170702-82-off466" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170702-82-off466" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18170702-82-cd467" type="crimeDate">24th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170702-82-off466 t18170702-82-cd467"></join>, two table cloths, value 7s.; one tea-spoon, value 3s.; and one 2l. bank note, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18170702-82-victim684" type="victimName">
                           George 
                           Harlow
                        <interp inst="t18170702-82-victim684" type="surname" value="Harlow"></interp>
