                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170702-82-defend682 t18170702-82-punish471"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 17.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before J. Vaillant, Esq.</p>
